{"tid":1613552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環午間散步，凝聚目光［中環返工，和理非入黎］","createTime":"2019-10-02T14:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T16:47:08.000Z","uid":301332,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"583f1f1d4bc99c61e9ae3ed3ffe60e31011393b6","tid":1613552,"uid":301332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:39:47.000Z","msg":"[朋友冇連登account，代轉發］<br />\n今日有幸親眼見證中環lunch time出現人潮高呼口號，實為和理非又一里程碑。<br />\n<br />\n面對政府以暴止亂，警隊濫用暴力，每況愈下，預見到既係只會變本加厲，可以如何對抗/反擊？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日日不合作運動，係<strong>每日</strong>呀</span></span>，直至抗爭勝利為止，話比政府聽你好唔妥佢！但香港人最鍾意返工，講罷講咗咁多次，次次都俾人話阻住返工乜乜乜。今日，終於為熱愛返工嘅和理非搵到佢哋嘅工作！就係每日都喺lunch time出去中環散步！<br />\n<br />\n中環係亞洲金融中心核心地帶，有ㄧ種極<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大象徵意義</span></strong></span>，仲有好多外國人，大機構，香港國際化既形象都係由中環代表。就好似衝擊立法會，雖然立法會只係ㄧ幢大廈，但背後象徵住香港立法權力核心位置！如果每日lunch time係中環行街，可以令到更多外資銀行/ 金融機構/ 遊客睇到&amp;關注我地既訴求，外媒一定會煲，施壓俾政府，堅定地話俾政府聽我地係唔會退，五大訴求，缺一不可！呢個係對準政權既象徵，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中環，If we burn, you burn with us!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n Keep住每日話比政府知，加大力度！<br />\n<br />\n作為出現係中環/ 附近區域既人，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係林鄭口中no stake既人</span></span>！我呼籲大家食飽飯落街散步！你知啦，中環人做野壓力大，散下步充下電曬下太陽好舒心的，凝聚中心力量！個心有唔舒服就嗌出黎！日日返工，日日散步！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你衝你又驚，遊行你又怕熱，又好鍾意返工，呢個活動你仲有咩藉口唔做？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n日期：一至五<br />\n時間：食飯時間一點正<br />\n路線：跟返今日，皇后像廣場（遮打道）&gt;畢打街&gt;干諾道中&gt;來回兜圈（路線開放討論）作為中環日常<br />\n事情：lunch time來回散步 嗌口號<br />\n<br />\n我唔代表任何人，只係我好希望用得能力去參與呢件事。呢場運動可貴在於民間自發、遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明天見，後天見，直到煲底見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efe862a070f3d079ce9e14ab9e7a7b85edf5895","tid":1613552,"uid":221055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:41:25.000Z","msg":"尖東友想組團<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbae9d1a9814bdd9acf5ae972aab5627a3f4fa10","tid":1613552,"uid":276551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:41:37.000Z","msg":"食飽要散吓步 如果唔係下晝好易恰眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f1cf3ac0b73ed6959c619286c556e946690914","tid":1613552,"uid":295761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:48:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14541993a2946fe73f9c5ad34d90ba779bfce311","tid":1613552,"uid":9570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:09:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"482b86807adbefdb5b4abf86cfb42d7a4b8f863f","tid":1613552,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:35:39.000Z","msg":"住附近嘅街坊食完晏都可以落行散步消化下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26194c3ceca24da11fbec1bc6c563f0d193b0ff","tid":1613552,"uid":277107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:50:15.000Z","msg":"今日成班西裝友行<br />\n其實好powerful"},{"pid":"f448ac9b5edb78ba82e3e065f570fd32af343130","tid":1613552,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:52:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fca7be24457072ba5e817ad7da70037af9cddbb1","tid":1613552,"uid":282449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:33:49.000Z","msg":"所有商業區有就好"},{"pid":"570c8b3e2f7b96715a14d6500f489c67256bf1b4","tid":1613552,"uid":267838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGKtBKh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGKtBKh.png&h=d4126f59&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}